Class DefaultRemoteRasterStore

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gvsig.tools.dispose.impl.AbstractDisposable
      • org.gvsig.raster.impl.store.AbstractRasterDataStore
        • org.gvsig.raster.impl.store.DefaultRasterStore
          • org.gvsig.raster.impl.store.DefaultRemoteRasterStore
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Histogramable, PyramidRasterStore, RasterDataStore, RasterStoreProperties, TRasterStore, DataFactoryUnit, DataStore, CoverageStore, CoverageStoreProviderServices, DataStoreInitializer, DataStoreProviderServices, Metadata, QueryableRaster, Disposable, DynObject, DynObject_v2, ComplexObservable, ComplexWeakReferencingObservable, Observable, WeakReferencingObservable, Persistent, Services, Visitable

    public class DefaultRemoteRasterStore
extends DefaultRasterStore
    This store represents a raster loaded from a remote service. This implements the interface RemoteRasterServiceStore to provide enough methods for this kind of services.
